[http://www.ampedwireless.com/products/rea20.html Product page] Per '''Amped Wireless'''' product page... *The device has one dual-band antenna and one dedicated antenna for each of the two bands. *This device uses four 5GHz 700mW 2-Stage amplifiers, two 2.4GHz amplifiers, and four ''advanced'' LNAs. *The processor clock speed is 660MHz. **This would seem to indicate the device is using RTL8197D.. which would not be unexpected. The Wi-Fi radio ASICs are likely RTL8812AR and RTL8192CE.
